3. Mandatory License Adoption:
All users, contributors, and forks must adopt the most recent version of this license. Continued use of any version of the software (past or future) after a license update constitutes acceptance of the new license.

4. Grace Period for License Refusal:
If any individual or organization does not agree to the updated license, they must:
- Cease use of the source code and derived software within 7 months.
- For server operators and hosted services, cease use within 12 months of the license update.

5. Copyright Transfer on Reuse:
